question: show me immigrants in each city
sql_query3: select Foreign_born_Population, Naturalized_Citizens, municipality from population
interpretation1: List the foreign born population per city.
interpretation2: List the naturalised citizen population per city.
interpretation3: List the foreign born and naturalised citizen population per city.

question: show me cities and immigrants where more than 60,000 people live
sql_query1: select municipality, Foreign_born_Population from population where Total_Population > 60000
sql_query2: select municipality, Naturalized_Citizens from population where Total_Population > 60000
sql_query3: select municipality, Foreign_born_Population, Naturalized_Citizens from population where Total_Population > 60000
interpretation1: Show me cities where more than 60,000 people live and foreign born population of that places.
interpretation2: Show me cities where more than 60,000 people live and naturalized citizens of that places.
interpretation3: Show me cities where more than 60,000 people live, along with their foreign born population and naturalized citizens of that places.
sql_query_general: select municipality, immigration_status from population where Total_Population > 60000
